Subject: [PATCH v5 2/5] x86/insn: Support big endian cross-compiles
Message-ID: <patch-2.thread-1e2854.git-3f5a9fe8c81f.your-ad-here.call-01605220128-ext-6070@work.hours>
References: <cover.thread-1e2854.your-ad-here.call-01605220128-ext-6070@work.hours>
